 Gustavus ( meanings=6 glosses=6 NOUN NOUN_PROPER_SINGULAR ) 
  Gustavus_I~1nz (king~5n) king of Sweden who established Lutheranism as the state religion
  Gustavus_Adolphus~1nz (king~5n) king of Sweden whose victories in battle made Sweden a European power
  Gustavus_III~1nz (king~5n) king of Sweden who increased the royal power and waged an unpopular war against Russia
  Gustavus_IV~1nz (king~5n) king of Sweden whose losses to Napoleon I led to his being deposed in 1809
  Gustavus_V~1nz (king~5n) king of Sweden who kept Sweden neutral during both World War I and II
  Gustavus_VI~1nz (king~5n) the last king of Sweden to have any real political power
